'''2010-12年洲際沙灘排球賽'''為[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會排球比賽|2012年奧運沙灘排球比賽]]的資格賽。本賽事從2010年6月1日開始，到2012年6月24日結束，比賽分為次區域、區域和洲際三個階段。





== 非洲 ==
{{main|2010-12年洲際沙灘排球賽-非洲}}
Teams will compete in the sub-zonal tournaments, with all teams advancing, with each team carrying over the points it earns to the five zonal tournament, where teams not entered in the sub-zonal tournaments can enter. The top team in each group plus top three runners up will advance to the continental cup.

== 亞洲/大洋洲 ==
{{main|2010-12年洲際沙灘排球賽-亞洲/大洋洲}}
41個亞洲級大洋洲國家參賽包括兩個非[[國際奧林匹克委員會|國際奧林匹克委員會]]會員國(澳門和北馬利安納群島)。<ref name="自动生成1">{{cite web|url=http://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=25832&Language=en|title=Tuvalu and Northern Mariana Islands headline Asia 2012 Olympic Games Beach Volleyball qualifying schedule|3=|accessdate=2011-07-30|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183513/http://www.fivb.org/viewPressRelease.asp?No=25832&Language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>次區域賽事的最前兩名晉級區域賽事，區域賽事的前三名將可晉級洲際賽事。<ref name="自动生成1" />

== 歐洲 ==
{{main|2010-12年洲際沙灘排球賽- 歐洲}}
Teams will be split into groups of four, where an elimiation bracket will determine the 3 teams to advance to the next stage from the sub-zones.

== 北美 ==
{{main|2010-12年洲際沙灘排球賽-北美}}
The North American zone see the sub zones divided into the [[Caribbean|Caribbean]], Central and Central American zones. The two Caribbean zones will meet and the central and Central American zones will meet in the zonal tournaments. Both Caribbean zones will have a elimination bracket where two teams per country competing in a two game series, if there is a tie a fifth game will be played by both countries. In the second round of the bracket the series will be a best of three. The winner and runner up of the main bracket and of the repechage will advance to the next round.

